                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <ol class="font_8 color_16" style="font-weight:bold;">
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To provide a generous selection of academic curricula and specialized programs in aviation science enriched with instruction in general education.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To provide the students with a background of experience and job skills which will enhance their employability.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To lead the students in the self-discovery process of clarifying and raising the individualâs goals and achievements commensurate with their potential.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To provide the students with the knowledge, skills and proficiency which contribute to success in their careers.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To make available to our students activities and experiences through various internships that will foster personal growth and leadership qualities that will assist students in their vocational, academic and social pursuits.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To provide a framework and atmosphere of learning which will enhance the studentâs capability to demonstrate ethical and moral values in professional and personal situations.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To strive for and maintain excellence in aviation and general education by continuously and systematically reviewing classroom facilities, equipment, curricula, faculty, and staff.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To provide placement assistance for graduates and students through individual counseling.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li>
                    <p class="font_8">
                     <span style="font-weight:bold;">
                      <span class="color_16">
                       To maintain a process of communication with the community of employers to assure relevant curricula to meet the developing needs of the aviation industry.
                      </span>
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                  </ol>
                 </div>
